<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Eric SJ Research</title><link>https://ericsj.xyz/zh-cn/</link><description>Recent content on Eric SJ Research</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 10 Jul 2026 00:34:58 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ericsj.xyz/zh-cn/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>从交易费到稳定币:Web3商业模式背后的收入驱动力与护城河</title><link>https://ericsj.xyz/zh-cn/web3/%E4%BB%8E%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E8%B4%B9%E5%88%B0%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%B8%81web3%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E8%83%8C%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%8E%E6%8A%A4%E5%9F%8E%E6%B2%B3/</link><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jul 2026 00:34:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ericsj.xyz/zh-cn/web3/%E4%BB%8E%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E8%B4%B9%E5%88%B0%E7%A8%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%B8%81web3%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E8%83%8C%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E9%A9%B1%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%E4%B8%8E%E6%8A%A4%E5%9F%8E%E6%B2%B3/</guid><description>Web3正在从“用户增长时代”，进入“商业模式验证时代”，上一篇文章我聊了五种已经被验证的 Web3 商业模式：。</description></item><item><title>从Hyperliquid到Tether：Web3已验证的5张现金流表</title><link>https://ericsj.xyz/zh-cn/web3/%E4%BB%8Ehyperliquid%E5%88%B0tetherweb3%E5%B7%B2%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%9A%845%E5%BC%A0%E7%8E%B0%E9%87%91%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%A8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 14:34:19 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ericsj.xyz/zh-cn/web3/%E4%BB%8Ehyperliquid%E5%88%B0tetherweb3%E5%B7%B2%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%9A%845%E5%BC%A0%E7%8E%B0%E9%87%91%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%A8/</guid><description>Web3 已验证的现金流主要来自交易费、稳定币储备收益、资金利差、区块空间与基础设施服务费。</description></item><item><title>NIKE直营退潮，分销渠道重新上桌？</title><link>https://ericsj.xyz/zh-cn/stocks/nike%E7%9B%B4%E8%90%A5%E9%80%80%E6%BD%AE%E5%88%86%E9%94%80%E6%B8%A0%E9%81%93%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%8A%E6%A1%8C/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jul 2026 12:04:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ericsj.xyz/zh-cn/stocks/nike%E7%9B%B4%E8%90%